## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "YouTube Download" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

Explore the following capabilities:

### YouTube Downloads

YouTube Download app allow you to download the audio and video files which you paste in the box when it met following criteria:
1. you have to use only the link copied from the youtube app and paste it here. It will never work if you copy from YT Music or anyother youtube link shared.
2. Video should be in public access.

### Save File

By Default the file will be saved in the Application directory Name which should be inside your files app. 


